description: This Chainlink VRF common Anurak purrs with a rating of 8, and a multiplier of 1x. It has a total score of 8, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are Nine Lives for North, 5 for East, 1 for South, and 8 for West. Anurak has the personality suit of hodler. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random packs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Anurak [8 Votes, Common]
